heading: Immortal Emanation Dungeon Guide
content: Immortal Emanation contains the , a fairly bad aspect not worth our time. Still, completing the dungeon once can help complete your Fractured Peaks Renown, but we don't recommend grinding this dungeon as it has a clunky layout and annoying monsters. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
